      <title>高盛认为中国将积蓄财政火力以应对特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/goldman-sees-china-saving-fiscal-firepower-to-prepare-for-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团称，唐纳德·特朗普可能已经影响了中国的经济议程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/goldman-sees-china-saving-fiscal-firepower-to-prepare-for-trump</guid>
